- ðŸ”¹ **User Progress Tracking**: Levels and XP are saved in your browser.
- ðŸ”¹ **Final Boss Stage**: Test your skills on a big challenge.
- ðŸ”¹ **Local Leaderboard**: Track your scores and compare with others.
- ðŸ”¹ **Firebase Authentication**: Login required to access stages.

## Pages

- `index.html` â€” Main page and login/register.
