## How to Play

1. Register an account on the main page.
2. Log in to access the **Cyber Arena**.
3. Complete stages by finding hidden messages, decoding challenges, or solving puzzles.
4. Level up and earn XP.
5. Fight the **Final Boss** when all stages are completed.
6. Track your progress on your profile and leaderboard.

## Technologies Used

- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Firebase Authentication
- GitHub Pages (hosting)

